# Cloudflare Web Analytics beacon site token — PUBLIC (it ships in the page HTML; not a secret).
# Minted by infra's bootstrap/analytics.tf (cloudflare_web_analytics_site) once NotAVibe-dev/infra#23
# is applied. Copy this file to .env and set the real value; it is then injected into the beacon in
# src/layouts/Base.astro and splash/index.html (same token for both sites).
PUBLIC_CF_WEB_ANALYTICS_TOKEN=
